column1: Preliminary Pokémon Listings Considered the Most Popular Ever
A Workbook as Written by Thomas Wiencek

The following is a list of Pokémon voted and/or selected the most popular ever by commercial website article editors, including their Rank number. These include honorable mentions (HM for short). The ratings are not all consistent, some are top 3, top 5, top 10, etc. At anytime if any of you users have general comments and/or suggestions on this Pokémon that you have listed here, and/or have submitted me commercial websites articles that show the most popular, best and/or strongest Pokémon ever including by type, generation, region and in-game availability, and various others, please contact to let me know by emailing me at tpwebmasterpiece@gmail.com, thanks. :)
